      </section>

      <section>
        <h2>2. Purpose of the site</h2>
        <p>
          monicamontufar.com is Mónica Montúfar's personal and professional website.
          Its purpose is to showcase her work, share editorial content about digital nomadism, travel and design,
          and facilitate contact with people interested in her services.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2>3. Intellectual property</h2>
        <p>
          All content on this site — texts, photographs, illustrations, logos, graphic design and source code —
          is the property of Mónica Montúfar or their respective authors, and is protected by applicable
