        </p>
        <p>
          Reproduction, distribution, transformation or public communication of any content without
          express written authorisation from the owner is prohibited.
          Quotations for informational or journalistic purposes are permitted provided the source is credited
          and the original content is linked.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2>4. Disclaimer</h2>
        <p>
          Mónica Montúfar does not guarantee the accuracy, completeness or currency of the information
          published on this site. Content is for informational purposes only and does not constitute
          professional advice of any kind (legal, financial, medical, etc.).
        </p>
        <p>
          This site may contain links to third-party websites. Mónica Montúfar is not responsible for the
          content or privacy practices of those sites.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2>5. Data protection</h2>
        <p>
          The processing of personal data collected through the contact form is described in the
          <a href="/en/politica-de-privacidad-y-cookies/">Privacy & Cookies Policy</a>.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2>6. Applicable law</h2>
        <p>
          This website operates from an international context (digital nomad owner with no fixed domicile).
          Any dispute arising from the use of the site shall be resolved in accordance with the general
          principles of law applicable in the user's jurisdiction, or by amicable agreement between the parties.
        </p>
      </section>

      <p class="text-sm text-white/40 mt-12">Last updated: May 2026</p>

    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
